title: Patsy.Cline.Video.Collection
description:
This collection of (very old) Patsy Cline videos was clipped out of a DVD release of a television documentary entitled "Patsy Cline: Sweet Dreams Still" (IMDB: tt0780580).

Well I happened to be doing a little housekeeping the other day and looking for things to delete. I'd seen the documentary already and didn't plan to watch it again, but I did want to keep the musical bits. So I clipped them out and here they are!

The audio and visual quality of these clips ranges from "very poor" to "decent". The majority being in the "decent" range I think. It's miraculous really, that these exist at all.

There are a few extras here that didn't appear in the television documentary broadcast, but came with the same DVD.

Also, I have numbered the files so as to mix them up a bit. There is no special meaning to the numbering.

Here is the track list:

01. Patsy Cline - A Church A Courtroom and Then Goodbye.avi
02. Patsy Cline - Come On In 1.avi
03. Patsy Cline - I've Loved And Lost Again (Ranch Party).avi
04. Patsy Cline - How Can I Face Tomorrow.avi
05. Patsy Cline - Walkin' After Midnight 1.avi
06. Patsy Cline - Let's Go To Church.avi
07. Patsy Cline - I Fall To Pieces.avi
08. Patsy Cline - Lovesick Blues.avi
09. Patsy Cline - She's Got You.avi
10. Patsy Cline - Three Cigarettes In An Ashtray.avi
11. Patsy Cline - San Antonio Rose.avi
12. Patsy Cline - Come On In 2.avi
13. Patsy Cline - Let It Snow.avi
14. Patsy Cline - Walkin' After Midnight 2.avi
15. Patsy Cline - So Wrong.avi
16. Patsy Cline - Crazy.avi

All files are XviD/AVI format at 4:3 aspect with an internal frame size of 720x480 (rendered 640x480).

Enjoy!

- user101966
